text: Wiebke Nulle is an archer from Germany. She was born on 5 June 1980. Nulle competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics.Wiebke NulleWiebke NULLE == References == Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:German archers Category:Olympians for Germany Category:Sportspeople from Lower Saxony
